**/fix-*.sh
**/error-fix-*.js
**/typescript-fixes.js
**/build-error-fixes.sh

# Delete marked files
**/**(delete)
**/**(edit - *)

# Documentation artifacts (keep main docs)
**/DEPLOYMENT_FIXES_NEEDED.md
**/ERROR_FIX_GUIDE.md
**/FIXES_APPLIED.md
**/TROUBLESHOOTING_OLD.md

# PM2 runtime files
**/.pm2/
**/pm2.log
